# TROUBLESHOOTING
# ============================================================================
# Bot won't start?
#   - Make sure DISCORD_TOKEN is set correctly
#   - Check that you enabled all required intents in Discord Developer Portal
#
# Bot can't read messages?
#   - Enable MESSAGE CONTENT INTENT in Discord Developer Portal
#
# Twitch integration not working?
#   - Verify all Twitch tokens are correct
#   - Check token hasn't expired (refresh if needed)
#   - Ensure channel IDs and guild ID are correct
#
# Spotify integration not working?
#   - Make sure spotipy is installed: pip install spotipy
#   - Verify client ID and secret are correct
#   - Check that refresh token is valid (may need to re-authorize)
#   - Ensure redirect URI matches in Spotify dashboard
